OL,3,CThousands to face disruption at
OL,4,CGatwick due to strike action
OL,6,FThere is set to be major disruption at
OL,7,FGatwick, the UK's second biggest
OL,8,Fairport, over the coming Easter
OL,9,Fweekend as over a hundred workers plan
OL,10,Fto strike over several issues
OL,11,Fincluding pensions not being paid.
OL,13,FThe strike involves Red Handling staff
OL,14,F- who are members of the Unite Union
OL,15,Fand includes baggage handlers, check-
OL,16,Fin staff and flight dispatchers.
OL,18,FGatwick says it's supporting the four
OL,19,Fairlines affected - Norwegian and
OL,20,FDelta, TAP and Air Peace.
