OL,3,CThousands to face disruption at
OL,4,CGatwick due to strike action
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Red Handling said
OL,7,Fthey are committed to their UK staff
OL,8,Fand have increased salaries by 22
OL,9,Fpercent in the past two years. The
OL,10,Ffirm says it wants to solve the
OL,11,Fdispute and will be doing its best to
OL,12,Fhelp passengers.
OL,14,F"We are working with all the
OL,15,Fstakeholders and feel confident on
OL,16,Ffinding a resolution. We are also
OL,17,Fconfident on our contingency plans to
OL,18,Fsupport safe and timely travel over
OL,19,Fthe Easter weekend."
